captain is very proud.

00:02:11.670 --> 00:02:13.820
Sir, it's about time.

00:02:13.820 --> 00:02:19.730
Oh, right. Sorry to have you 
stop by when you're so busy.

00:02:21.550 --> 00:02:24.410
