00:16:13.970 --> 00:16:19.040
Let's negotiate. Why not join us?

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:20.120
Join you?

00:16:20.120 --> 00:16:22.670
Yes, it'll be quite fun.

00:16:22.670 --> 00:16:26.740
That sounds tempting... But I'll pass.

00:16:26.740 --> 00:16:29.550
I swore my loyalty to the 
Wizard King, after all.

00:16:29.550 --> 00:16:33.700
I see. That's unfortunate.

00:16:42.380 --> 00:16:44.390
Looks like I already paid you back.

00:16:46.830 --> 00:16:48.910
It truly is unfortunate

00:16:48.910 --> 00:16:52.730
that there were traitors 
among the Magic Knights.

00:16:58.990 --> 00:17:01.790
Now, all that's left is...

00:17:02.540 --> 00:17:04.000
Yeah.

00:17:08.990 --> 00:17:11.340
I don't know who the hell 
that is, but take him down!

00:17:15.900 --> 00:17:18.620
I wasn't planning on interfering,

00:17:18.620 --> 00:17:20.790
but I think I'm allowed 
to have a <i>little</i> fun.

00:17:27.340 --> 00:17:28.690
The hell?

00:17:30.740 --> 00:17:32.360
Well done.

00:17:32.760 --> 00:17:38.120
You were able to capture the traitors 
as well as all of the bandits.

00:17:38.120 --> 00:17:41.370
I mean... the bandits' boss was 
out cold at the top of the tree.

00:17:43.110 --> 00:17:45.370
I guess weirder things have happened.

00:17:45.940 --> 00:17:48.950
Again, excellent work.

00:17:48.950 --> 00:17:49.920
By the way...

00:17:52.430 --> 00:17:54.300
Yami, Vangeance...

00:17:54.980 --> 00:17:57.150
Considering everything you've done so far,

00:17:57.930 --> 00:18:01.300
I'm appointing both of you 
as captains of new squads.

00:18:01.660 --> 00:18:03.330
You're making us...

00:18:03.330 --> 00:18:05.560
...captains of new squads?

00:18:06.530 --> 00:18:07.810
Will you accept my offer?

00:18:12.090 --> 00:18:15.590
I guess the competition to see who can 
become squad captain first ended in a draw.

00:18:15.590 --> 00:18:18.360
Yes, but our true competition 
still lies ahead.

00:18:18.360 --> 00:18:19.310
Yeah.

00:18:19.850 --> 00:18:20.850
I won't lose.

00:18:20.850 --> 00:18:21.830
Neither will I.

00:18:22.210 --> 00:18:27.080
I believe in both of you. Yami, 
what kind of squad will you create?

00:18:27.080 --> 00:18:30.170
What kind of squad? Let's see...

00:18:30.610 --> 00:18:36.000
A squad where status, bloodlines, 
and social standing don't matter.

00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:41.340
I'll round up some outsiders and hooligans, 
and create a place where they can belong.

00:18:41.690 --> 00:18:44.170
Just like you did for me.

00:18:44.170 --> 00:18:46.350
Sure. That sounds great!

00:18:46.350 --> 00:18:50.150
I'll call them... Let's see...

00:18:50.150 --> 00:18:54.450
I'll gather up a bunch of guys who all 
have their own color, mix them all up,

00:18:54.450 --> 00:18:56.870
and once their colors all mix together...

00:18:57.490 --> 00:18:59.810
Black. The Black Hooligans?

00:18:59.810 --> 00:19:01.660
Nah, let's go with bulls.

00:19:01.660 --> 00:19:04.370
Okay, I'll call them the Black Bulls!

00:19:04.370 --> 00:19:06.350
The Black Bulls...

00:19:06.350 --> 00:19:08.760
That sounds perfect for you.

00:19:08.760 --> 00:19:09.710
And you?

00:19:09.710 --> 00:19:12.610
I will create the Golden Dawn.

00:19:12.610 --> 00:19:13.710
The Golden...?

00:19:13.710 --> 00:19:18.130
Yes. Creating the ultimate squad is 
my way of repaying you, Lord Julius.

00:19:18.770 --> 00:19:19.740
As the name suggests,

00:19:19.740 --> 00:19:24.730
I will make a squad that will bring 
a golden dawn to this world.

00:19:25.510 --> 00:19:27.510
Even though the night is dark,

00:19:27.510 --> 00:19:31.630
I will prove that the light will always shine,
 and a golden dawn will come one day.

00:19:31.630 --> 00:19:33.900
How cheesy can you be?

00:19:34.330 --> 00:19:37.710
That sounds wonderful, too.
I look forward to it.

00:19:37.710 --> 00:19:42.860
Starting today, you are the Captain of the 
Golden Dawn. Congratulations, William.

00:19:42.860 --> 00:19:43.660
Thank you, sir.

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:51.500
And starting today, you are the Captain of 
the Magic Knights Squad, the Black Bulls.

00:19:51.500 --> 00:19:52.920
Congratulations, Yami.

00:19:56.920 --> 00:19:59.050
Looking forward to working with you, Goldie.

00:20:04.450 --> 00:20:05.550
So there you have it.

00:20:06.630 --> 00:20:07.740
Right...

00:20:08.030 --> 00:20:09.180
What'd you think?

00:20:09.180 --> 00:20:12.620
Um... I guess you went through a lot.

00:20:12.620 --> 00:20:15.230
So, what were you trying to say?

00:20:15.790 --> 00:20:18.180
Even if you stumble, 
even if you think you might lose,

00:20:18.180 --> 00:20:20.310
you'll be fine as long as you don't give up!

00:20:20.310 --> 00:20:22.220
Don't ever give up in any situation!

00:20:22.220 --> 00:20:23.570
Surpass your limits!

00:20:23.570 --> 00:20:25.610
Then a path will always open up for you!

00:20:25.610 --> 00:20:28.660
Quit being so depressed just because 
you lost to your rival once!

00:20:28.660 --> 00:20:31.830
Even if you lose 99 times, you just 
have to win the next time!

00:20:31.830 --> 00:20:36.290
I-I see... You should've just 
said that in the first pla—

00:20:36.290 --> 00:20:37.460
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!

00:20:37.460 --> 00:20:40.050
Captain! You're going to crush my skull!

00:20:40.770 --> 00:20:43.730
But Captain Yami's right!

00:20:43.730 --> 00:20:45.510
There's no point in being depressed!

00:20:45.510 --> 00:20:49.900
All right! I'm gonna catch 
up to Yuno and surpass him!

00:20:50.630 --> 00:20:51.680
Come to think of it,

00:20:52.030 --> 00:20:56.440
shouldn't we be getting the results from 
the Royal Knights Selection Exam soon?

00:20:56.750 --> 00:21:00.940
O-Oh, yeah... I-I can't wait!

00:21:01.460 --> 00:21:04.130
Come on, messenger owls!

00:21:06.570 --> 00:21:09.580
The hell? That's no messenger owl.

00:21:11.020 --> 00:21:13.630
I dunno who the hell you are,
 but stop that racket!

00:21:13.630 --> 00:21:16.210
Don't you know that this is the 
home of the Black Bulls,

00:21:16.210 --> 00:21:18.380
the Magic Knights Squad that Mister Yami—

00:21:18.380 --> 00:21:20.380
Th-The heck?!

00:21:24.050 --> 00:21:27.890
Y-You're Lady Sisgoleon!

00:22:58.940 --> 00:23:03.440
Petit Clover

00:22:59.900 --> 00:23:02.550
Petit Clover!

00:23:02.940 --> 00:23:06.940
Golden Weird Mask Guy!

00:23:03.860 --> 00:23:05.810
Golden Weird Mask Guy!

00:23:06.940 --> 00:23:09.260
Say, Golden Weird Mask Guy.

00:23:09.260 --> 00:23:11.400
I'd rather you didn't call me that.

00:23:11.400 --> 00:23:12.200
Then...

00:23:12.200 --> 00:23:14.130
Baldie Weird Mask Guy.

00:23:14.130 --> 00:23:16.580
I'd rather you didn't call me that, either.

00:23:16.580 --> 00:23:18.550
Baldie Long Drawers Mask Guy!

00:23:18.550 --> 00:23:19.830
Please stop.

00:23:20.210 --> 00:23:22.300
Baldie Long Drawers Belly Warmer Mask Guy!

00:23:22.300 --> 00:23:24.210
This doesn't even make sense anymore.

00:23:24.540 --> 00:23:27.220
Baldie Long Drawers Belly Warmer 
Tiny Mustache Mask Guy!

00:23:27.220 --> 00:23:28.590
How long is this going to go on?

00:23:28.590 --> 00:23:31.960
Baldie Long Drawers Belly 
Warmer Tiny Mustache...

00:23:31.960 --> 00:23:34.700
who wears his shirt and 
socks backwards... Mask Guy?

00:23:33.540 --> 00:23:34.700
No, really. How long?

00:23:34.700 --> 00:23:36.340
How about Birthday Suit Mask Guy?

00:23:40.080 --> 00:23:42.940
It's finally time to find out the results 
of the Royal Knights Selection Exam!

00:23:42.940 --> 00:23:45.730
I know for damn sure that I was chosen!

00:23:45.730 --> 00:23:47.440
Who are you calling worried?!

00:23:47.440 --> 00:23:51.110
Next time on <i>Black Clover</i>, Page 87: 
"Formation of the Royal Knights."

00:23:48.570 --> 00:23:54.250
Page 87
 Formation of the Royal Knights

00:23:51.110 --> 00:23:52.660
I'm fired up!